results.name: Swap (2,3) and all twin prime pairs >(3,5) in prime factorization of n.
comment: a(a(n))=n, self-inverse permutation of natural numbers; a(n)=n for single primes (A007510) and products of twin prime pairs (A037074).
link: Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
formula: Multiplicative with a(p) = (if p<=3 then 5-p else (if p+2 is prime then p+2 else (if p-2 is prime then p-2 else p))), p prime.
results.author: _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Jun 07 2002
